# D{{N}} — Coupling & Volatility Matrix

**Audience:** Architect (re-modelling conversations).
**When to look at this:** When considering a BC merge, a BC split, a Separate Ways re-classification, or estimating the blast radius of a change. Also: post-incident reviews where coupling was implicated.
**Prose gap closed:** `7-context-map.md` lists edges as a flat table; this matrix shows the **N×N coupling distribution** with volatility deltas, exposing pairs that should not be coupled given how differently they change.

